Module Generations
Package main.model.generation.ecosystems

Class ANaturalEcosystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.model.generation.ecosystems.ANaturalEcosystem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEcosystem
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FightingEcosystem, MatchmakingEcosystem
    public abstract class ANaturalEcosystem
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEcosystem
    The base class of natural ecosystems, where organisms dynamically interact, or in other words generations are not static. This is meant to mimic natural generations, where the best-suited organisms survive and reproduce.
    Author:
    jhwang73
